<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="140" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="11.[136,1452,1166,1661]" pageId="11" pageNumber="140">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,478,1598,1624]" pageId="11" pageNumber="140">Distribution and habitat</emphasis>
:―This subspecies is endemic to the island of Kithira, where it grows on coastal habitats and stony places in phrygana communities.
</paragraph>
